            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Rutil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Marcellinus pa<lb break="no" n="2"/>tri matri fratribus et <lb n="3"/>sororibus nepties <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>nepot<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>b</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>et</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> <expan><abbr>Icaro</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> filius <note>sic</note> Mario <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">I</supplied> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>diutricis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>qui <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> IXXX <expan><abbr>me</abbr><ex cert="low">nses</ex></expan> V <expan><abbr>di</abbr><ex cert="low">es</ex></expan> X SIF<lb break="no" n="6"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex cert="low"/>IVS</expan><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex cert="low"/>IVS</expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan><expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex cert="low">ses</ex></expan> I fili <note>sic</note> meae <note>sic</note> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>t M<supplied reason="lost">ar</supplied>tiniano filiem <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>praes</abbr><ex cert="low">entem</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <lb n="8"/>qui <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> XXXV me<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> V dies XIII <lb n="9"/>et Aur<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ia</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>iugi</abbr></expan> eius qui <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>X me<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> IIII dies V parentes vivi po<lb break="no" n="11"/>suerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Lesung unsicher (CIL III: &amp;quot;&amp;quot;litteris malis&amp;quot;&amp;quot;). Z. 4: ET-Ligatur zu Beginn oder Licaro? Die Deutung von Z. 4 ist unklar. MARIO als korrumpierte Chargenbezeichnung des Icarus/Licarus? Oder Icaro, filius(!) Mario(!)? Z. 6: [fi]lius? Z. 7: praec(edentem)(!)? Z. 10: Bemerkenswert wäre das niedrige Alter der Gattin des Martinianus mit 10 Jahren, sofern dieses richtig überliefert ist.</p>
            </div>
